	   <tr><td colspan=2>Thanks for posting that Calliopeia, saved me cutting and pasting :)<br><br>Effect is nice, and well worth it.&nbsp;&nbsp;For me at 65, with VotS and epic, it was stripping high end shammy DoT's in one pulse.  It's a targettable song, meaning you need to target yourself to remove the DoT, but hopefully that means you wont need to be in group to hit others.<br><br>Seemed powerful to me, as I said.  From memory, it removes about 9 or 10 disease counters at a time, which is a pretty decent amount.  The curse one should be similar as well.<br><br>BTW, jus to finish off my post that Calli put in, Jusean Evanesque is outside the bard guild in south qeynos - once you give the book to Kardin, you run to Qeynos, give the book to Jusean and run back to Kardin.  That final hand in to Kardin gets you the song.<br><br>Grunter Tonedeth<br>Maestro of Frayed Knot<br>The Rathe<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=325897" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=325897</a><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
